{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0149HbX2pPQH7kkfg74Hc8HF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Quarkus 3.30.5 -> Spring Boot 3.2.5\n\n**Overall Outcome:** SUCCESS - Application builds, runs, and all 13 smoke tests pass.\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus BOM/dependencies with Spring Boot starter parent and starters\n- Dockerfile: Changed build to `mvn clean package` and run to `java -jar` Spring Boot fat JAR\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Converted Quarkus config to Spring Boot properties\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/AddressBookApplication.java: Spring Boot main class\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/entity/Contact.java: JPA entity (preserved)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/repository/ContactRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/service/ContactService.java: Service layer\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/controller/ContactController.java: Spring MVC controller\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/controller/ContactApiController.java: REST API controller\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/controller/HomeController.java: Home page controller\n- src/main/resources/templates/index.html: Thymeleaf index template\n- src/main/resources/templates/contact/List.html: Contact list template\n- src/main/resources/templates/contact/Create.html: Contact create form\n- src/main/resources/templates/contact/Edit.html: Contact edit form\n- src/main/resources/templates/contact/View.html: Contact view template\n- src/main/resources/static/css/jsfcrud.css: Static CSS (moved from META-INF)\n- smoke.py: 13 smoke tests covering REST API and web UI\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/ (entire package): All Quarkus-specific Java code\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/: All JSF templates, web.xml, faces-config.xml\n- src/main/resources/Bundle.properties: JSF resource bundle\n- src/main/resources/ValidationMessages.properties: JSF validation messages\n- src/main/resources/mvnw, mvnw.cmd: Stale copies\n```\n\n### Key Migration Decisions\n\n1. **JSF -> Thymeleaf**: JSF is tightly coupled to its servlet container and has no Spring Boot support. Thymeleaf is the standard Spring Boot template engine.\n2. **EJB Facade -> Spring Service + Repository**: Replaced `AbstractFacade<T>` + `ContactFacade` with `JpaRepository` + `@Service` -- the idiomatic Spring pattern.\n3. **Added REST API**: Created `/api/contacts` endpoints alongside the web UI for programmatic access and smoke testing.\n4. **Package rename**: `quarkus.tutorial.addressbook` -> `com.example.addressbook` to follow Spring Boot conventions.\n\n### Error Handling\n- **Error Summary:** 0 errors during migration\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":349,"cache_read_input_tokens":114943,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":349,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":782},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"817510db-4945-42e9-9845-9e09f3fea89b","uuid":"a5aa3dde-c865-44de-b86a-104cd6dcbac8"}
