s/Bundle.properties: JSF resource bundle\n- src/main/resources/ValidationMessages.properties: JSF validation messages\n- src/main/resources/mvnw, mvnw.cmd: Stale copies\n```\n\n### Key Migration Decisions\n\n1. **JSF -> Thymeleaf**: JSF is tightly coupled to its servlet container and has no Spring Boot support. Thymeleaf is the standard Spring Boot template engine.\n2. **EJB Facade -> Spring Service + Repository**: Replaced `AbstractFacade<T>` + `ContactFacade` with `JpaRepository` + `@Service` -- the idiomatic Spring pattern.\n3. **Added REST API**: Created `/api/contacts` endpoints alongside the web UI for programmatic access and smoke testing.\n4. **Package rename**: `quarkus.tutorial.addressbook` -> `com.example.addressbook` to follow Spring Boot conventions.\n\n### Error Handling\n- **Error Summary:** 0 errors during migration\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None","session_id":"817510db-4945-42e9-9845-9e09f3fea89b","total_cost_usd":9.876334830000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":51,"cache_creation_input_tokens":102849,"cache_read_input_tokens":3666984,"output_tokens":30802,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":102849}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":98054,"outputTokens":5128,"cacheReadInputTokens":158461,"cacheCreationInputTokens":20822,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.13245408000000003,"contextWindow":200000},"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":517,"outputTokens":168,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.004071,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":51,"outputTokens":30802,"cacheReadInputTokens":3666984,"cacheCreationInputTokens":102849,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":9.739809750000003,"contextWindow":200000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"98b31c20-1ddf-4736-be94-9d442a8f3708"}
